name: Nami v2 [9mb]
description:
TRIGGER TAG: namiOP


Optinal tags:

one piece

bikini, blue pants (for her clasic outfit)

orange hair, long hair, brown eyes (add this tags if the character doesn't look like nami)

This model was trained on nai-pruned using 100+ images, but it work best on anything-v4.5 and AbyssOrangeMix2.
all images with different art styles. the goal of this model is to be very flexible.

and there it is, my first lora, hope you like it.
